videos.headline: Jackson helps power Louisville over Kentucky
videos.description: ESPN's Dave Neal and Matt Stinchcomb break down how even though Kentucky got off to a hot start, Louisville QB Lamar Jackson was able to bring his team back to defeat the Wildcats 38-24.
